    <item>
      <title>菲律宾再次尝试通过医用大麻法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/philippines-tries-again-to-pass-bill-on-medical-cannabis-use</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾众议院于周二批准了一项允许将大麻用于医疗目的的法案，此前该法案曾多次尝试失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/philippines-tries-again-to-pass-bill-on-medical-cannabis-use</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 03:09:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国逮捕涉嫌泄露间谍名单的官员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/south-korea-arrests-official-for-suspected-leak-of-spy-list</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国逮捕了一名官员，他涉嫌泄露包括派驻海外的秘密特工名单在内的国防情报，这促使韩国军方下令将所有海外特工撤回国内以确保安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/south-korea-arrests-official-for-suspected-leak-of-spy-list</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 03:04:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯将于下周携副总统候选人开启战场州之旅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/harris-to-launch-battleground-state-tour-with-vp-pick-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡玛拉·哈里斯和她尚未公布姓名的竞选搭档将于下周开始访问七个战场州，希望在美国大选中抓住机会对抗共和党人唐纳德·特朗普。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/harris-to-launch-battleground-state-tour-with-vp-pick-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 01:35:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊曼纽尔大使称无论选举结果如何，美日同盟都将保持稳固</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/us-japan-alliance-robust-regardless-of-election-ambassador-rahm-emanuel-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华盛顿驻日本特使表示，深化美日安全一体化将有助于确保两国关系无论政治如何变化都能保持强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/us-japan-alliance-robust-regardless-of-election-ambassador-rahm-emanuel-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 01:09:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚最大州政府为推动自治而剥离天然气资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/malaysia-s-biggest-state-carves-out-gas-assets-in-autonomy-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚最大的州砂拉越将从联邦政府运营的公司手中接管其天然气资产的控制权，该州争取经济自治的运动在该东南亚国家脆弱的政治局势中取得了成果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/malaysia-s-biggest-state-carves-out-gas-assets-in-autonomy-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 01:00:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯承诺签署唐纳德·特朗普反对的边境法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/harris-pledges-to-sign-border-bill-as-team-eyes-georgia-voters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯在佐治亚州的一次集会上承诺就美墨边境问题达成两党协议，试图减弱其竞争对手唐纳德·特朗普的攻击路线，并解决其竞选活动中最大的政治负担之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/harris-pledges-to-sign-border-bill-as-team-eyes-georgia-voters</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 23:44:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国确认拨款创纪录的15亿英镑支持绿色能源</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-confirms-record-1-5-billion-budget-to-support-green-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国将在即将举行的拍卖会上拨款创纪录的 15 亿英镑（19 亿美元）用于支持新的可再生能源发电能力，这是政府努力消除电网碳排放的关键一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/uk-confirms-record-1-5-billion-budget-to-support-green-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列瞄准的真主党指挥官长期以来一直被美国通缉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/hezbollah-commander-targeted-by-israel-long-sought-by-us-for-1983-beirut-bombing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列在贝鲁特针对真主党指挥官实施报复性火箭弹袭击，而这位指挥官还因40多年前在同一城市制造爆炸事件而被美国通缉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/hezbollah-commander-targeted-by-israel-long-sought-by-us-for-1983-beirut-bombing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 23:00:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普和哈里斯的广告将焦点集中在 2024 年竞选新方案中的五个州</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/trump-harris-ad-buys-focus-on-five-states-in-revamped-2024-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普和副总统卡玛拉·哈里斯将 98% 的广告购买火力集中在五个摇摆州，这是双方竞选团队如何制定入主白宫战略的一个关键指标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-30/trump-harris-ad-buys-focus-on-five-states-in-revamped-2024-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 22:40:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
